<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><entry xmlns:functx="http://www.functx.com" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="entry_ærvgænæn" xml:lang="os"><form type="lemma"><orth>ærvgænæn</orth></form><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>дверной засов, запор</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>doorband, door lock</q></cit></sense><cit type="exampleGroup"><cit type="example"><quote>gænaxy dwar ærvgænænæj mīdægæj cyrd æræxkædtoj</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>ворота крепости поспешно заперли изнутри засовом</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>the stronghold gates were hastily locked with a bar on the inside</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Хар._Кадӕг"/><biblScope>64</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><cit type="exampleGroup"><cit type="example"><quote>gænaxy dwar ærvgænænæj mīdægæj cyrd æræxkædtoj</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>ворота крепости поспешно заперли изнутри засовом</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>the stronghold gates were hastily locked with a bar on the inside</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Хар._Кадӕг"/><biblScope>64</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><etym xml:lang="ru">Производное от неупотребительного составного глагола *%iærf (ærv) kænyn%i ‘запирать на засов’, как <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æxkænæn"/> ‘запор’ от %iæx-kænyn%i ‘запирать’. *%iÆrf%i возводится к <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>arpa-</w></mentioned>; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/><w>arp-(arpayati)</w><gloss><q>втыкать</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘засовывать’, ‘скреплять’.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">This is a derivate form of a complex verb *%iærf (ærv) kænyn%i ‘to bolt’ which is out of use, the same derivation process is to be found in <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æxkænæn"/> 'lock' from %iæx-kænyn%i ‘to lock’. *%iÆrf%i traces back to <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>arpa-</w></mentioned>; compare <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/><w>arp- (arpayati)</w><gloss><q>to stick into</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘to put into’, ‘to fasten’.</etym></entry>